{"page_url": "https://www.gamespot.com/articles/god-of-war-ragnarok-all-berserker-gravestone-locations/1100-6508926/", "page_title_en": "God of War Ragnarok All Berserker Gravestone Locations", "page_title_ko": "", "page_title_cn": "", "page_description_en": "There are quite a few of these, and the enemies you encounter will pose a serious threat.", "page_description_ko": "", "page_description_cn": "", "page_author": "Billy Givens", "page_date": "2022-11-08T21:00:00-0800", "page_text_html": "\n                <p>You'll have quite a lot of side quests to complete as you explore the nine realms found in <a href=\"/games/god-of-war-ragnarok/\" data-ref-id=\"5000-519021\">God of War Ragnarok</a>. Known as Favors, these optional objectives can sometimes actually be an extremely important part of your gear and weapon progression. One such Favor is \"<strong>Fit for a King</strong>,\" which you'll start during the Main Quest \"The Word of Fate.\" This Favor requires you to seek out Berserker Gravestones across the nine realms and defeat the Berserker bosses within. There are <strong>10 total Berserker Gravestones</strong>, but some of them feature multiple bosses at one time, so be prepared for a serious showdown.</p><p>Completing most of the Berserker Gravestones is probably best saved for post-game cleanup due to the intense challenge of each boss and the fact that a handful of the gravestones aren't accessible until much, much later, such as a particular Berserker Gravestone in Alfheim. When you are ready to seek them out, though, be sure you bring a Ressurection Stone and upgrade your gear as much as possible. If you discover you just can't take down one of the bosses, feel free to go tackle another and revisit the gravestone when you've leveled up some more. But whether you're planning to wait or dive in immediately, here's where you can find each Berserker Gravestone.</p><p><strong>Consider this guide to contain spoilers for late- and post-game content.</strong></p><h2>Berserker Gravestone locations</h2><p>Below are the locations of each Berserker Gravestone and its respective boss(es).</p><h3>Midgard - The Lake of Nine</h3><figure data-align=\"center\" data-size=\"large\" data-img-src=\"https://www.gamespot.com/a/uploads/original/679/6794662/4060247-godofwarragnar%C3%B6k_20221108134057.jpg\" data-ref-id=\"1300-4060247\" data-ratio=\"0.5625\" data-width=\"3840\" data-embed-type=\"image\" style=\"width: 3840px\"><a class=\"fluid-height\" style=\"padding-bottom:56.3%\" href=\"https://www.gamespot.com/a/uploads/original/679/6794662/4060247-godofwarragnar%C3%B6k_20221108134057.jpg\" data-ref-id=\"1300-4060247\"><img alt=\"The Lake of Nine\" src=\"https://www.gamespot.com/a/uploads/scale_super/679/6794662/4060247-godofwarragnar%C3%B6k_20221108134057.jpg\" srcset=\"https://www.gamespot.com/a/uploads/original/679/6794662/4060247-godofwarragnar%C3%B6k_20221108134057.jpg 3840w, https://www.gamespot.com/a/uploads/scale_super/679/6794662/4060247-godofwarragnar%C3%B6k_20221108134057.jpg 1280w, https://www.gamespot.com/a/uploads/scale_medium/679/6794662/4060247-godofwarragnar%C3%B6k_20221108134057.jpg 480w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 1280px) 100vw, 1280px\" data-width=\"1280\"></a><figcaption>The Lake of Nine</figcaption></figure><p><strong>Boss:</strong> Fraekni the Zealous</p><p>For defeating this boss, you'll receive Berserker Waist Guard, 2 Tempered Remnants, 25 Bonded Leather, and 25 Shattered Runes.</p><h3>Svartalfheim - Jarnsmida Pitmines</h3><figure data-align=\"center\" data-size=\"large\" data-img-src=\"https://www.gamespot.com/a/uploads/original/679/6794662/4060248-godofwarragnar%C3%B6k_20221108134120.jpg\" data-ref-id=\"1300-4060248\" data-ratio=\"0.5625\" data-width=\"3840\" data-embed-type=\"image\" style=\"width: 3840px\"><a class=\"fluid-height\" style=\"padding-bottom:56.3%\" href=\"https://www.gamespot.com/a/uploads/original/679/6794662/4060248-godofwarragnar%C3%B6k_20221108134120.jpg\" data-ref-id=\"1300-4060248\"><img alt=\"Jarnsmida Pitmines\" src=\"https://www.gamespot.com/a/uploads/scale_super/679/6794662/4060248-godofwarragnar%C3%B6k_20221108134120.jpg\" srcset=\"https://www.gamespot.com/a/uploads/original/679/6794662/4060248-godofwarragnar%C3%B6k_20221108134120.jpg 3840w, https://www.gamespot.com/a/uploads/scale_super/679/6794662/4060248-godofwarragnar%C3%B6k_20221108134120.jpg 1280w, https://www.gamespot.com/a/uploads/scale_medium/679/6794662/4060248-godofwarragnar%C3%B6k_20221108134120.jpg 480w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 1280px) 100vw, 1280px\" data-width=\"1280\"></a><figcaption>Jarnsmida Pitmines</figcaption></figure><p><strong>Bosses:</strong> Starolfr the Troublesome, Bodvar the Fierce</p><p>For defeating these bosses, you'll receive Hind of the Nine Realms, Gale Flame, 5 Tempered Remnants, 80 Bonded Leather, and 75 Shattered Runes.</p><h3>Svartalfheim - Nidavellir</h3><figure data-align=\"center\" data-size=\"large\" data-img-src=\"https://www.gamespot.com/a/uploads/original/679/6794662/4060249-godofwarragnar%C3%B6k_20221108134142.jpg\" data-ref-id=\"1300-4060249\" data-ratio=\"0.5625\" data-width=\"3840\" data-embed-type=\"image\" style=\"width: 3840px\"><a class=\"fluid-height\" style=\"padding-bottom:56.3%\" href=\"https://www.gamespot.com/a/uploads/original/679/6794662/4060249-godofwarragnar%C3%B6k_20221108134142.jpg\" data-ref-id=\"1300-4060249\"><img alt=\"Nidavellir\" src=\"data:image/gif;base64,R0lGODlhAQABAAAAACH5BAEKAAEALAAAAAABAAEAAAICTAEAOw==\" sizes=\"(max-width: 1280px) 100vw, 1280px\" data-width=\"1280\" class=\"js-lazy-load-image\" data-src=\"https://www.gamespot.com/a/uploads/scale_super/679/6794662/4060249-godofwarragnar%C3%B6k_20221108134142.jpg\" data-srcset=\"https://www.gamespot.com/a/uploads/original/679/6794662/4060249-godofwarragnar%C3%B6k_20221108134142.jpg 3840w, https://www.gamespot.com/a/uploads/scale_super/679/6794662/4060249-godofwarragnar%C3%B6k_20221108134142.jpg 1280w, https://www.gamespot.com/a/uploads/scale_medium/679/6794662/4060249-godofwarragnar%C3%B6k_20221108134142.jpg 480w\" data-lazy-load=\"false\"><noscript><img alt=\"Nidavellir\" src=\"https://www.gamespot.com/a/uploads/scale_super/679/6794662/4060249-godofwarragnar%C3%B6k_20221108134142.jpg\" srcset=\"https://www.gamespot.com/a/uploads/original/679/6794662/4060249-godofwarragnar%C3%B6k_20221108134142.jpg 3840w, https://www.gamespot.com/a/uploads/scale_super/679/6794662/4060249-godofwarragnar%C3%B6k_20221108134142.jpg 1280w, https://www.gamespot.com/a/uploads/scale_medium/679/6794662/4060249-godofwarragnar%C3%B6k_20221108134142.jpg 480w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 1280px) 100vw, 1280px\" data-width=\"1280\"></noscript></a><figcaption>Nidavellir</figcaption></figure><p><strong>Boss:</strong> Hardrefill the Callous</p><p>For defeating this boss, you'll receive Asgard's Fortitude, 2 Tempered Remnants, 25 Bonded Leather, and 25 Shattered Runes.</p><h3>Svartalfheim - Alberich Island</h3><figure data-align=\"center\" data-size=\"large\" data-img-src=\"https://www.gamespot.com/a/uploads/original/679/6794662/4060250-godofwarragnar%C3%B6k_20221108134205.jpg\" data-ref-id=\"1300-4060250\" data-ratio=\"0.5625\" data-width=\"3840\" data-embed-type=\"image\" style=\"width: 3840px\"><a class=\"fluid-height\" style=\"padding-bottom:56.3%\" href=\"https://www.gamespot.com/a/uploads/original/679/6794662/4060250-godofwarragnar%C3%B6k_20221108134205.jpg\" data-ref-id=\"1300-4060250\"><img alt=\"Alberich Island\" src=\"data:image/gif;base64,R0lGODlhAQABAAAAACH5BAEKAAEALAAAAAABAAEAAAICTAEAOw==\" sizes=\"(max-width: 1280px) 100vw, 1280px\" data-width=\"1280\" class=\"js-lazy-load-image\" data-src=\"https://www.gamespot.com/a/uploads/scale_super/679/6794662/4060250-godofwarragnar%C3%B6k_20221108134205.jpg\" data-srcset=\"https://www.gamespot.com/a/uploads/original/679/6794662/4060250-godofwarragnar%C3%B6k_20221108134205.jpg 3840w, https://www.gamespot.com/a/uploads/scale_super/679/6794662/4060250-godofwarragnar%C3%B6k_20221108134205.jpg 1280w, https://www.gamespot.com/a/uploads/scale_medium/679/6794662/4060250-godofwarragnar%C3%B6k_20221108134205.jpg 480w\" data-lazy-load=\"false\"><noscript><img alt=\"Alberich Island\" src=\"https://www.gamespot.com/a/uploads/scale_super/679/6794662/4060250-godofwarragnar%C3%B6k_20221108134205.jpg\" srcset=\"https://www.gamespot.com/a/uploads/original/679/6794662/4060250-godofwarragnar%C3%B6k_20221108134205.jpg 3840w, https://www.gamespot.com/a/uploads/scale_super/679/6794662/4060250-godofwarragnar%C3%B6k_20221108134205.jpg 1280w, https://www.gamespot.com/a/uploads/scale_medium/679/6794662/4060250-godofwarragnar%C3%B6k_20221108134205.jpg 480w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 1280px) 100vw, 1280px\" data-width=\"1280\"></noscript></a><figcaption>Alberich Island</figcaption></figure><p><strong>Boss:</strong> Beigadr the Feared</p><p>For defeating this boss, you'll receive Asgard's Might, 2 Tempered Remnants, 25 Bonded Leather, and 25 Shattered Runes.</p><h3>Alfheim - The Barrens</h3><figure data-align=\"center\" data-size=\"large\" data-img-src=\"https://www.gamespot.com/a/uploads/original/679/6794662/4060252-godofwarragnar%C3%B6k_20221108134226.jpg\" data-ref-id=\"1300-4060252\" data-ratio=\"0.5625\" data-width=\"3840\" data-embed-type=\"image\" style=\"width: 3840px\"><a class=\"fluid-height\" style=\"padding-bottom:56.3%\" href=\"https://www.gamespot.com/a/uploads/original/679/6794662/4060252-godofwarragnar%C3%B6k_20221108134226.jpg\" data-ref-id=\"1300-4060252\"><img alt=\"The Barrens\" src=\"data:image/gif;base64,R0lGODlhAQABAAAAACH5BAEKAAEALAAAAAABAAEAAAICTAEAOw==\" sizes=\"(max-width: 1280px) 100vw, 1280px\" data-width=\"1280\" class=\"js-lazy-load-image\" data-src=\"https://www.gamespot.com/a/uploads/scale_super/679/6794662/4060252-godofwarragnar%C3%B6k_20221108134226.jpg\" data-srcset=\"https://www.gamespot.com/a/uploads/original/679/6794662/4060252-godofwarragnar%C3%B6k_20221108134226.jpg 3840w, https://www.gamespot.com/a/uploads/scale_super/679/6794662/4060252-godofwarragnar%C3%B6k_20221108134226.jpg 1280w, https://www.gamespot.com/a/uploads/scale_medium/679/6794662/4060252-godofwarragnar%C3%B6k_20221108134226.jpg 480w\" data-lazy-load=\"false\"><noscript><img alt=\"The Barrens\" src=\"https://www.gamespot.com/a/uploads/scale_super/679/6794662/4060252-godofwarragnar%C3%B6k_20221108134226.jpg\" srcset=\"https://www.gamespot.com/a/uploads/original/679/6794662/4060252-godofwarragnar%C3%B6k_20221108134226.jpg 3840w, https://www.gamespot.com/a/uploads/scale_super/679/6794662/4060252-godofwarragnar%C3%B6k_20221108134226.jpg 1280w, https://www.gamespot.com/a/uploads/scale_medium/679/6794662/4060252-godofwarragnar%C3%B6k_20221108134226.jpg 480w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 1280px) 100vw, 1280px\" data-width=\"1280\"></noscript></a><figcaption>The Barrens</figcaption></figure><p><strong>Bosses:</strong> Svipdagr the Cold, 2 Sisters of Illska</p><p>For defeating these bosses, you'll receive Frozen Flame, Asgard\u2019s Security, Berserker Cuirass, 5 Tempered Remnants, 180 Bonded Leather, and 75 Shattered Runes.</p><h3>Alfheim - The Forbidden Sands</h3><figure data-align=\"center\" data-size=\"large\" data-img-src=\"https://www.gamespot.com/a/uploads/original/679/6794662/4060253-godofwarragnar%C3%B6k_20221108134246.jpg\" data-ref-id=\"1300-4060253\" data-ratio=\"0.5625\" data-width=\"3840\" data-embed-type=\"image\" style=\"width: 3840px\"><a class=\"fluid-height\" style=\"padding-bottom:56.3%\" href=\"https://www.gamespot.com/a/uploads/original/679/6794662/4060253-godofwarragnar%C3%B6k_20221108134246.jpg\" data-ref-id=\"1300-4060253\"><img alt=\"The Forbidden Sands\" src=\"data:image/gif;base64,R0lGODlhAQABAAAAACH5BAEKAAEALAAAAAABAAEAAAICTAEAOw==\" sizes=\"(max-width: 1280px) 100vw, 1280px\" data-width=\"1280\" class=\"js-lazy-load-image\" data-src=\"https://www.gamespot.com/a/uploads/scale_super/679/6794662/4060253-godofwarragnar%C3%B6k_20221108134246.jpg\" data-srcset=\"https://www.gamespot.com/a/uploads/original/679/6794662/4060253-godofwarragnar%C3%B6k_20221108134246.jpg 3840w, https://www.gamespot.com/a/uploads/scale_super/679/6794662/4060253-godofwarragnar%C3%B6k_20221108134246.jpg 1280w, https://www.gamespot.com/a/uploads/scale_medium/679/6794662/4060253-godofwarragnar%C3%B6k_20221108134246.jpg 480w\" data-lazy-load=\"false\"><noscript><img alt=\"The Forbidden Sands\" src=\"https://www.gamespot.com/a/uploads/scale_super/679/6794662/4060253-godofwarragnar%C3%B6k_20221108134246.jpg\" srcset=\"https://www.gamespot.com/a/uploads/original/679/6794662/4060253-godofwarragnar%C3%B6k_20221108134246.jpg 3840w, https://www.gamespot.com/a/uploads/scale_super/679/6794662/4060253-godofwarragnar%C3%B6k_20221108134246.jpg 1280w, https://www.gamespot.com/a/uploads/scale_medium/679/6794662/4060253-godofwarragnar%C3%B6k_20221108134246.jpg 480w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 1280px) 100vw, 1280px\" data-width=\"1280\"></noscript></a><figcaption>The Forbidden Sands</figcaption></figure><p><strong>Boss:</strong> Hjalti the Stolid</p><p>This one is a bit tricky to access, so use our Alfheim Berserker Gravestone guide for more details. For defeating this boss, you'll receive Grip of the Nine Realms, 3 Tempered Remnants, 40 Bonded Leather and 40 Shattered Runes.</p><h3>Vanaheim - Pilgrim\u2019s Landing</h3><figure data-align=\"center\" data-size=\"large\" data-img-src=\"https://www.gamespot.com/a/uploads/original/679/6794662/4060255-godofwarragnar%C3%B6k_20221108134310.jpg\" data-ref-id=\"1300-4060255\" data-ratio=\"0.5625\" data-width=\"3840\" data-embed-type=\"image\" style=\"width: 3840px\"><a class=\"fluid-height\" style=\"padding-bottom:56.3%\" href=\"https://www.gamespot.com/a/uploads/original/679/6794662/4060255-godofwarragnar%C3%B6k_20221108134310.jpg\" data-ref-id=\"1300-4060255\"><img alt=\"Pilgrim's Landing\" src=\"data:image/gif;base64,R0lGODlhAQABAAAAACH5BAEKAAEALAAAAAABAAEAAAICTAEAOw==\" sizes=\"(max-width: 1280px) 100vw, 1280px\" data-width=\"1280\" class=\"js-lazy-load-image\" data-src=\"https://www.gamespot.com/a/uploads/scale_super/679/6794662/4060255-godofwarragnar%C3%B6k_20221108134310.jpg\" data-srcset=\"https://www.gamespot.com/a/uploads/original/679/6794662/4060255-godofwarragnar%C3%B6k_20221108134310.jpg 3840w, https://www.gamespot.com/a/uploads/scale_super/679/6794662/4060255-godofwarragnar%C3%B6k_20221108134310.jpg 1280w, https://www.gamespot.com/a/uploads/scale_medium/679/6794662/4060255-godofwarragnar%C3%B6k_20221108134310.jpg 480w\" data-lazy-load=\"false\"><noscript><img alt=\"Pilgrim's Landing\" src=\"https://www.gamespot.com/a/uploads/scale_super/679/6794662/4060255-godofwarragnar%C3%B6k_20221108134310.jpg\" srcset=\"https://www.gamespot.com/a/uploads/original/679/6794662/4060255-godofwarragnar%C3%B6k_20221108134310.jpg 3840w, https://www.gamespot.com/a/uploads/scale_super/679/6794662/4060255-godofwarragnar%C3%B6k_20221108134310.jpg 1280w, https://www.gamespot.com/a/uploads/scale_medium/679/6794662/4060255-godofwarragnar%C3%B6k_20221108134310.jpg 480w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 1280px) 100vw, 1280px\" data-width=\"1280\"></noscript></a><figcaption>Pilgrim's Landing</figcaption></figure><p><strong>Boss:</strong> Hvitserkr the Bold</p><p>For defeating this boss, you'll receive Pommels of the Nine Realms, 3 Tempered Remnants, 25 Bonded Leather, and 40 Shattered Runes.</p><h3>Vanaheim - The Sinkholes</h3><figure data-align=\"center\" data-size=\"large\" data-img-src=\"https://www.gamespot.com/a/uploads/original/679/6794662/4060256-godofwarragnar%C3%B6k_20221108134353.jpg\" data-ref-id=\"1300-4060256\" data-ratio=\"0.5625\" data-width=\"3840\" data-embed-type=\"image\" style=\"width: 3840px\"><a class=\"fluid-height\" style=\"padding-bottom:56.3%\" href=\"https://www.gamespot.com/a/uploads/original/679/6794662/4060256-godofwarragnar%C3%B6k_20221108134353.jpg\" data-ref-id=\"1300-4060256\"><img alt=\"The Sinkholes\" src=\"data:image/gif;base64,R0lGODlhAQABAAAAACH5BAEKAAEALAAAAAABAAEAAAICTAEAOw==\" sizes=\"(max-width: 1280px) 100vw, 1280px\" data-width=\"1280\" class=\"js-lazy-load-image\" data-src=\"https://ww